Get documents from a docket folder

get_documents.Rd

get_documents("[docketId]") retrieves metadata for all documents belonging to a docket

Usage

get_documents(docketId, lastModifiedDate, api_keys)

Arguments

docketId

ID of docket

lastModifiedDate

Filter results by their last modified date. Default is set to Sys.time().

User-specified values must be formatted as yyyy-MM-dd%20HH:mm:ss.

api_keys

API key(s) from api.data.gov.

Details

Value

References

Author

Note

See also
